00:16:34.166 --> 00:16:37.066
we have no right over Mother’s time.

319
00:16:38.199 --> 00:16:39.999
No one in this universe has the right.

320
00:16:48.000 --> 00:16:48.933
That is correct.

321
00:16:49.566 --> 00:16:52.266
Now,  the first time I was in Delhi,

322
00:16:53.533 --> 00:16:56.533
I saw that some sindoor was kept in a plastic container.

323
00:16:57.766 --> 00:16:59.800
And they got a plastic mug from

324
00:16:59.800 --> 00:17:01.233
some bathroom to wash My Feet.

